Credits First:-
99.8% DragonKK for the files. 0.1% Alex for help. (Other Alex). 0.1% Me for writing this tutorial.
Download the Server and Client files from here:- http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,552262.0.html
Download another 667 Server and Client. For an example, I'm posting NRS3, but any one will do:- http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,548954.0.html
Extract all the files, then go into the other 667 server files. Copy the libs folder into the Matrix server files folder.
Do the same with the client, copy the 667 client libs folder into the 718 client folder.
Enjoy your working source with no errors. If you need any run's or whatnot, use these.
Server Run:
@echo off title Matrix echo Launching Server... "C:/Program Files/Java/jre7/bin/java.exe" -Xmx512m -cp bin;lib/*; com.rs.Launcher true true false pause
Server Compile:
@echo off title Matrix Compiler echo Compiling Matrix.. "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.7.0_04\bin\javac.exe" -d bin -cp lib/*; -sourcepath src src/com/rs/*.java @echo Finished. pause
Client Compiler:
@echo off title compile "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.7.0_04/bin/javac" -cp lib/*; -d bin -sourcepath src src/client.java "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.7.0_04/bin/javac" -cp lib/*; -d bin -sourcepath src src/Loader.java @pause
Client Run;
@echo off "C:\Program Files\Java\jre7\bin\java.exe" -Xmx256m -Xss2m -Dsun.java2d.noddraw=true -XX:CompileThreshold=1500 -Xincgc -XX:+UseConcMarkSweepGC -XX:+UseParNewGC -cp bin;./clientlibs.jar; Loader pause
Et voila.
